      <p begin="00:18:58,963" end="00:19:00,000">Jeg tigger ikke, men det er t&#230;t p&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:00,000" end="00:19:00,700"/>
      <p begin="00:19:03,700" end="00:19:04,400">- Brugt t&#248;j?</p>
      <p begin="00:19:04,400" end="00:19:05,970">- Brugt t&#248;j er tilladt.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:05,970" end="00:19:07,097">- Aha!</p>
      <p begin="00:19:07,097" end="00:19:11,141">- Ingen nye stoffer men Michelle,<br/>jeg tror jeg vil tage en kold tyrker.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:11,141" end="00:19:13,602">- I hele &#229;ret, vil jeg ikke k&#248;be<br/>noget som helst hele &#229;ret.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:13,957" end="00:19:15,563">Det have v&#230;ret virkeligt fantastisk<br/>at slippe det</p>
