      <p begin="00:19:28,993" end="00:19:34,081"/>
      <p begin="00:19:34,081" end="00:19:34,999">- Ja, godt g&#229;et!</p>
      <p begin="00:19:34,999" end="00:19:39,746">- I starten, fordi det var vores vane <br/>at se TV, s&#229; vi savnede det.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:39,746" end="00:19:42,264">Og nu er det hul fyldt <br/>med at leve i nuet</p>
