      <p begin="00:20:25,424" end="00:20:26,717">OK. Kys mor farvel.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:26,717" end="00:20:28,302">- Jeg elsker dig!</p>
      <p begin="00:20:28,302" end="00:20:29,803">Vi ses senere, OK skat.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:29,803" end="00:20:31,388">Jeg tager p&#229; arbejde.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:31,388" end="00:20:46,153"/>
      <p begin="00:20:46,153" end="00:20:49,990">- Jeg s&#230;tter et indl&#230;g p&#229; bloggen med <br/>titlen "S&#229;dan undg&#229;r vi at skabe affald."</p>
      <p begin="00:20:49,990" end="00:20:53,202">Ingen indisk mad og smid-v&#230;k<br/>take-out bakker.</p>
