      <p begin="00:22:54,823" end="00:22:56,492">S&#229;, nu bev&#230;ger vi os ind i --</p>
      <p begin="00:22:56,492" end="00:22:57,201">- OK.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:57,201" end="00:22:58,520">- Du ved, v&#230;re sikker p&#229;<br/>at vi ikke har</p>
