      <p begin="00:24:38,217" end="00:24:39,282">Men, men hvis jeg ikke pr&#248;ver det...</p>
      <p begin="00:24:39,282" end="00:24:40,189">- OK.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:40,189" end="00:24:41,411">- Jeg ved ikke det hele.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:41,411" end="00:24:42,552">- Aha.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:42,552" end="00:24:43,538">- Der ser du.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:43,538" end="00:24:45,158"/>
      <p begin="00:24:45,158" end="00:24:46,714">- Aha.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:46,714" end="00:24:49,432">Hvad er det slemme <br/>ved toiletpapir?</p>
      <p begin="00:24:49,878" end="00:24:53,264">- Vi har bruge for vores tr&#230;er<br/>til at opsuge CO2 men i stedet,</p>
