      <p begin="00:25:16,797" end="00:25:20,538">som vi smider v&#230;k.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:20,538" end="00:25:24,113">- I aften t&#230;nkte jeg, OK alts&#229;<br/>hvis du beder mig g&#248;re dette,</p>
