      <p begin="01:27:36,349" end="01:27:39,668">- Det har v&#230;ret-- alts&#229;, det har <br/>ikke helt v&#230;ret et &#229;r</p>
      <p begin="01:27:39,668" end="01:27:43,349">fordi fasen med elektricitet<br/>startede omkring m&#229;ned seks.</p>
      <p begin="01:27:43,349" end="01:27:45,631">S&#229;, det har v&#230;ret seks m&#229;neder<br/>siden vi sidst havde str&#248;m.</p>
      <p begin="01:27:45,631" end="01:27:50,622">S&#229;, det er taknemmelighed <br/>for de sm&#229; forn&#248;jelser.</p>
      <p begin="01:27:50,622" end="01:27:52,262">- &#197;hhh.</p>
      <p begin="01:27:52,262" end="01:27:54,989">- Jah!</p>
      <p begin="01:27:54,989" end="01:27:57,311"/>
      <p begin="01:28:01,927" end="01:28:04,253"/>
      <p begin="01:28:05,956" end="01:28:07,677">- S&#229; g&#229;r det l&#248;s.</p>
      <p begin="01:28:07,677" end="01:28:16,949"/>
      <p begin="01:28:16,949" end="01:28:20,755">- Jeg m&#229; sige, jeg var ret skeptisk<br/>omkring mange ting i starten</p>
      <p begin="01:28:20,755" end="01:28:21,956">og jeg t&#230;nkte at de var sindsyge</p>
      <p begin="01:28:21,956" end="01:28:27,305">og virkelig dumme og jeg hadede <br/>og afskyede dig, skiftevis, for dem.</p>
      <p begin="01:28:27,305" end="01:28:30,765">Men, jeg vil virkelig, <br/>virkelig beholde cyklingen.</p>
      <p begin="01:28:30,765" end="01:28:34,502">Jeg vil beholde s&#229; meget som vi<br/>overhovedet kan med at undg&#229; affald.</p>
      <p begin="01:28:34,502" end="01:28:38,401">Og jeg vil virkelig ,virkelig <br/>beholde turene ti ltorvet.</p>
      <p begin="01:28:38,401" end="01:28:42,678"/>
      <p begin="01:28:42,678" end="01:28:46,953">Jeg vil v&#230;re vegetar<br/>men jeg vil have en hotdog af og til.</p>
      <p begin="01:28:46,953" end="01:28:48,246"/>
      <p begin="01:28:48,246" end="01:28:53,335">Jeg ville v&#230;re en vege-hogian <br/>eller en vege-dogian.</p>
      <p begin="01:28:53,335" end="01:28:57,779"/>
      <p begin="01:28:57,779" end="01:29:02,201">Jeg vil gerne undv&#230;re TV i huset,<br/>men jeg gl&#230;der mig til at g&#229; i biografen</p>
      <p begin="01:29:02,201" end="01:29:04,306">og n&#229;r vi er p&#229; ferie,<br/>er det p&#229; programmet.</p>
      <p begin="01:29:06,163" end="01:29:08,160">Det er nogle ting,<br/>som jeg har nogle problemer med.</p>
      <p begin="01:29:08,160" end="01:29:08,877">-Ja.</p>
      <p begin="01:29:08,877" end="01:29:10,640">- Hvorfor kan vi ikke g&#229; bort fra<br/>det med ormene?</p>
      <p begin="01:29:10,640" end="01:29:14,578">Fordi de laver<br/>Fluernes Herre i k&#248;kkenet.</p>
      <p begin="01:29:14,578" end="01:29:18,325">Og der er ogs&#229; nogle ting som<br/>vi bare skal kunne g&#248;re</p>
      <p begin="01:29:18,325" end="01:29:21,928">m&#229;ske og det er muligvis en af dem.</p>
      <p begin="01:29:21,928" end="01:29:24,039">For jeg skal ogs&#229; bestemme <br/>lidt her omkring.</p>
      <p begin="01:29:24,039" end="01:29:28,039"/>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
